73578_3779432585996644834_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=lN2IpXW1IkUQ7kNvgF0f3X7&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDyKzHQ-Y_isVu6vlDtGeknAIKcuHBxC36vT1gV0Fdsvw&oe=66F80733"}]}, "id": "690696038457085", "locale": "zh_CN", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "\u72fc\u4e0e\u8f9b\u9999\u6599\uff36\uff32\uff12", "keywords": ["\u52a8\u753b", "anime"], "long_description": "At the end of his journey with the wolf goddess Holo, former traveling merchant Lawrence settled down with her and opened a bathhouse.\nThe couple was blessed with an adorable daughter and an idyllic life.\nHowever, the beautiful wolves have a weakness for delicious meals and their food expenses are a source of headaches for Lawrence.\nOne day, as Lawrence is going about his fur side business to further fill the family's coffers, a slight incident occurs.\nTo further complicate things, Holo saunters in with quite the feast.\n\nThis is a VR Animation of Spice and Wolf: Spring Log, sequel to the original Spice and Wolf VR animation.\nThe game has a 30 minute story and a game mode where you can watch part of the anime alongside its characters in the style of Japanese paper street theater.\nA peaceful life in the bathhouse with wolfgirls awaits.\n", "short_description": "The team behind the original series has gotten together to bring you into the world of Spice and Wolf again for a second installment of VR animation! \nAnimation has evolved from \"watching\" to \"experiencing.\""}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Oculus_Portrait_en.png", "id": "3340538496025801", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75196229_3340538499359134_4352870022877613097_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rQE-YaKfp4cQ7kNvgGoKoJ6&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCDUn-VvtISai6bZNIjgGGotJz-c38h-N062GbgI0lMJg&oe=66F7EC85"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Hero_en.png", "id": "2781740535482777"